flowchart TD
    Route[Route starts long operation] --> Create[Create job in memory]
    Create --> Dict[(jobs dict)]
    Create --> Thread[Start daemon thread]
    Thread --> Context[Push Flask app context]
    Context --> Work[Run job function]
    Work --> Progress[Update progress and message]
    Progress --> Dict
    Work --> CancelCheck{Cancel requested}
    CancelCheck -- Yes --> Cancelled[Set status cancelled]
    CancelCheck -- No --> Finish{Work succeeded}
    Finish -- Yes --> Completed[Set status completed]
    Finish -- No --> Failed[Set status failed and error]
    Dict --> Poll[GET /job-status/job_id]
    Poll --> UI[Update browser progress]
    Completed --> Cleanup[Cleanup old finished jobs]
    Failed --> Cleanup
    Cancelled --> Cleanup
